thread.title: Joseph C.
thread.title_full: Wainscoting America reviewed by Joseph C.

author: Joseph C.
title: Joseph C.
text:
I'm not sure if my words can match my satisfaction with Wainscoting America customer service and their products. Diana was superb! She walked me through the design and ordering process and the installation was flawless. The on line tutorial for painting was excellent and added to the overall beauty of the finished project. Thank you so much
Joseph Colangelo
